    pageTitle: 'Disclaimer',
    lead: 'A few honest notes about how we write, what we can and cannot promise, and how we handle outside content.',
    lastUpdatedLabel: 'Last updated',
    sections: [
      {
        heading: 'Accuracy of information',
        body: [
          'We take care when researching and writing about Japanese words, phrases, and cultural context. That said, language is alive: nuances shift, new expressions appear, and regional usage varies.',
